sequenceDiagram
    participant VLLMPod as vLLM/SGLang Pod<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ PUB
    participant ZMQSub as ZMQ Subscriber<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ SUB
    participant Pool as KV-Events Pool<br/>(4 sharded workers)
    participant Adapter as Engine Adapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as Block Index<br/>(InMemory/Ristretto/Redis)
    participant EPP as EPP Scheduler<br/>(Host Process)
    participant Indexer as KV-Cache Indexer<br/>(Go Library)
    participant TokenPool as Tokenization Pool
    participant UDSTok as UDS Tokenizer<br/>gRPC (UDS socket)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over VLLMPod,Index: Flow 1: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
        VLLMPod->>ZMQSub: BlockStored/BlockRemoved/AllBlocksCleared<br/>ZMQ msgpack, 5557/TCP, No Encryption
        ZMQSub->>Pool: Raw ZMQ message<br/>(in-process Go channel)
        Note over Pool: FNV-1a hash of pod ID<br/>→ deterministic worker assignment
        Pool->>Adapter: Decode message<br/>(msgpack → Go struct)
        Adapter->>Index: Add(engineKey, requestKey, podID)<br/>or Evict(engineKey)
        Note over Index: Dual-key mapping:<br/>engineKey ↔ requestKey
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over EPP,Index: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
        EPP->>Indexer: ScoreTokens(modelID, tokens, candidates)<br/>(in-process Go API)
        Indexer->>TokenPool: Tokenize prompt (if needed)
        TokenPool->>UDSTok: gRPC Tokenize request<br/>UDS socket, No Encryption
        UDSTok->>UDSTok: vLLM OpenAIServingRender<br/>(CPU mode)
        UDSTok-->>TokenPool: Token IDs
        TokenPool-->>Indexer: Token IDs
        Note over Indexer: Compute FNV-64a block hashes<br/>from token chunks
        Indexer->>Index: Lookup(requestKeys)
        Index-->>Indexer: Pod → block hit map
        Note over Indexer: Score candidates by<br/>prefix cache coverage
        Indexer-->>EPP: map[podID]float64 scores
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over UDSTok,HFHub: Flow 3: Tokenizer Initialization
        UDSTok->>HFHub: Download tokenizer model files<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, HF Token (optional)
        HFHub-->>UDSTok: Tokenizer files
        Note over UDSTok: Cache tokenizer locally<br/>in TOKENIZERS_DIR
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 245)
        Note over VLLMPod,Index: Flow 4: KV-Cache Offloading (fs_backend)
        Note over VLLMPod: vLLM OffloadingConnector API
        VLLMPod->>VLLMPod: llmd_fs_backend<br/>StorageOffloadingHandlers
        Note over VLLMPod: GPU → Host memory copy<br/>(C++/CUDA)
        VLLMPod->>VLLMPod: Write KV blocks to<br/>Shared Storage (POSIX I/O)
        Note over VLLMPod: PVC Evictor manages<br/>disk space (N+2 processes)
    end
